:{{DIcon}} What's Serval up to these days?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501030005: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P20131/F20131001_G86/Act/Act_501030005.json-->
::'''Gepard:''' Same old, same old. Hunkered down at her workshop, either working on orders or dragging Pela and Lynx to rehearsals.
::'''Gepard:''' But, after that trip to Everwinter Hill, I don't think I've noticed her looking all glum anymore. I reckon she's sorted her troubles out.
::'''Gepard:''' And this was all thanks to your help, (Trailblazer). I thank you on my big sister's behalf.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} We're friends, and that's what we do.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030040-->
:::'''Gepard:''' Humility is a virtue. And with your courage and kindness... if we had someone like you among our ranks, it would be Belobog's utmost honor.
:::'''Gepard:''' As for me... I am immensely honored to have known a friend like you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It was your companionship that changed her.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030043-->
:::'''Gepard:''' ...Perhaps so. It heartens me to see her go back to her usual carefree self.
:::'''Gepard:''' In any case, I am truly thankful and honored to have such a friend as you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It looks like you really care for your big sis!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030046-->
:::'''Gepard:''' ...I don't.
:::'''Gepard:''' I'm merely performing the base duty required of a family member.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Whatever you say.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030049-->
::::'''Gepard:''' Thanks for understanding.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Aww, stop deflecting.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030051-->
::::'''Gepard:''' I... This...
::::'''Gepard:''' Ahem, I'm not deflecting.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Stop making things so awkward!
