::::'''Gepard:''' Why do you say the same thing as Big Sis... How am I making anything awkward?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501030055-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030055-->
:::'''Gepard:''' Regardless, us siblings have received much hospitality from you... it is truly an honor to have a friend such as you.
