:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030013-->
:::'''Gepard:''' Anything you can think of, the Silvermane Guards are responsible for.
:::'''Gepard:''' Above all else, the Captain is charged with organizing the Guards, ensuring that everyone performs their job properly.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I understand.
