::{{DIcon|Talk}} How's your relationship with your big sister?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030022-->
:::'''Gepard:''' Serval... I can only turn a blind eye to her various actions.
:::'''Gepard:''' To the Landaus, my big sister's acts are irrefutably traitorous to the clan. It is no wonder our butler regularly goes to the workshop to persuade her to find a proper job.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I hear Pela is your aide?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501030025-->
:::'''Gepard:''' Yes, but our interactions mostly revolve around work. Though, she is quite close to Serval, which is to say, our lives do somewhat intersect outside of work.
:::'''Gepard:''' In truth, I try to avoid her most of the time... I always feel that she's sort of hmm... overbearing.
:::'''Gepard:''' There was once when I saw that she was swamped with work, so I suggested helping her finish up a report.
:::'''Gepard:''' When I submitted it to her, I didn't think she'd be able to point out so many mistakes at a mere glance, followed by a barrage of detailed remarks...
:::'''Gepard:''' She personally apologized to me after that, and I also acknowledged my tardiness, but that matter sure taught me a lesson... It's best not to get involved in Pela's work.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
